Package: vibe
Title: Visualization and Exploration of Bulk RNA Sequencing data
Version: 0.12
Authors@R: 
    c(person("Saskia", "van Asten", , "saas@genmab.com", role = "aut"),
    person("Indu", "Khatri", , "inkh@genmab.com", role = "aut"),
    person("Francis", "Blokzijl", , "frbl@genmab.com", role = "aut"),
    person("Leandro", "Moreno", "lemo@genmab.com", role = "edt"),
    person("Iris", "Kolder", , "iko@genmab.com", role = c("aut","cre")))
Description: The VIBE package is developed to easily visualize bulk RNAseq or EdgeSeq datasets, for which log2 tpm/cpm is already calculated elsewhere. This package includes functions to generate tables with summary statistics (mean/median), per-gene boxplots, scatterplots for co-expression, and heatmaps.
